       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYMENTS.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.

           SELECT PAY-FILE  ASSIGN TO  PAYFILE
           ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
           FILE STATUS IS FS1.
           SELECT LOAN-FILE ASSIGN TO  LOANFILE
           ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
           ACCESS MODE IS RANDOM
           RECORD KEY IS LOAN-ID
           FILE STATUS IS FS2.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.

       FD   PAY-FILE.
       01   PAY-REC.
            05 P-TRANS-ID     PIC X(11).
            05 P-LOAN-ID      PIC X(6).
            05 P-CUST-ID      PIC X(5).
            05 P-NAME         PIC X(10).
            05 P-STATUS       PIC X(8).
            05 P-ACT-AMT      PIC 9(6).
            05 P-AMT-PAID     PIC 9(6).
            05 P-PAY-TYPE     PIC X.
            05 P-YORN         PIC X.
            05 BEST           PIC X(26).
       FD   LOAN-FILE.
       01   LOAN-REC.
            05 LOAN-ID         PIC X(6).
            05 CUST-ID         PIC 9(5).
            05 SANC-AMT        PIC 9(6).
            05 EMI-START       PIC X(10).
            05 EMI-END         PIC X(10).
            05 INTEREST        PIC 9(2).
            05 EMI-AMT         PIC 9(6).
            05 GRACE-DAYS      PIC 9(2).
            05 PENALTY-AMT     PIC 9(3).
            05 PAY-MODE       PIC X(2).
            05 TODAY-STATUS    PIC X.
            05 PROC-DATE       PIC X(10).
            05 TOTAL-PAID      PIC 9(6).
            05 NEXT-DUE        PIC 9(6).
            05 STATUS1         PIC X(6).
            05 TENURE          PIC 9(3).
            05 OVERDUE-AMT     PIC 9(6).
            05 NO-OF-EMI       PIC 9(3).
            05 FORECLOSURE     PIC 9(6).
            05 DUE-DAYS        PIC 9(3).
            05 DUE-AMT         PIC 9(6).
            05 RISK-SCORE      PIC XX.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 FS1               PIC XX.
       01 FS2               PIC XX.
       01 WS-EOF            PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01 WS-EXTRA          PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 WS-TOTAL-COLL     PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 EXTRA-DAYS        PIC 9(2).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MAIN-PARA.

           OPEN INPUT PAY-FILE
           OPEN I-O   LOAN-FILE
           DISPLAY FS1 FS2
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF = 'Y'

              READ PAY-FILE
                 AT END
                    MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF
                 NOT AT END

                    PERFORM PROCESS-PAYMENT
              END-READ

           END-PERFORM

           DISPLAY 'TOTAL COLLECTION TODAY = ' WS-TOTAL-COLL

           CLOSE PAY-FILE LOAN-FILE

           STOP RUN.


       PROCESS-PAYMENT.
           MOVE P-LOAN-ID TO LOAN-ID
           DISPLAY P-LOAN-ID LOAN-ID FS2
           READ LOAN-FILE KEY IS LOAN-ID
                INVALID KEY
                           DISPLAY 'LOANID NOT FOUND'
                NOT INVALID KEY
                          DISPLAY 'WORKING'
                          PERFORM LOAN-PARA
           END-READ.
        LOAN-PARA.
           DISPLAY LOAN-REC
           DISPLAY FS2
      *------ ADD TO TOTAL COLLECTION --------------------------------*

           ADD P-AMT-PAID TO WS-TOTAL-COLL

      *------ DETERMINE PAYMENT TYPE ---------------------------------*
           DISPLAY P-PAY-TYPE
           EVALUATE P-PAY-TYPE

           WHEN 'A'

               SUBTRACT 1 FROM NO-OF-EMI
               ADD P-AMT-PAID TO TOTAL-PAID
               MOVE 'Y' TO TODAY-STATUS
               SUBTRACT P-AMT-PAID FROM OVERDUE-AMT
               MOVE EMI-AMT TO NEXT-DUE

           WHEN 'P'

               SUBTRACT 1 FROM NO-OF-EMI
               ADD P-AMT-PAID TO TOTAL-PAID
               SUBTRACT P-AMT-PAID FROM OVERDUE-AMT
               COMPUTE NEXT-DUE = P-ACT-AMT - P-AMT-PAID + EMI-AMT
               MOVE 'Y' TO TODAY-STATUS

           WHEN 'E'

               ADD P-AMT-PAID TO TOTAL-PAID
               SUBTRACT P-AMT-PAID FROM OVERDUE-AMT
               COMPUTE EXTRA-DAYS = P-AMT-PAID / EMI-AMT
               MOVE 'Y' TO TODAY-STATUS
              IF DUE-DAYS > 0
               IF DUE-DAYS > EXTRA-DAYS
                  COMPUTE DUE-DAYS =  DUE-DAYS - EXTRA-DAYS
                  MOVE 0 TO EXTRA-DAYS
               ELSE
                  COMPUTE EXTRA-DAYS =  EXTRA-DAYS - DUE-DAYS
                  MOVE 0 TO DUE-DAYS
               END-IF
               IF EXTRA-DAYS = 0
                  CONTINUE
               ELSE
                  SUBTRACT EXTRA-DAYS FROM NO-OF-EMI
               END-IF
              ELSE
                SUBTRACT EXTRA-DAYS FROM NO-OF-EMI
              END-IF
           WHEN 'R'
                 CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
               DISPLAY 'INVALID PAYMENT TYPE'

           END-EVALUATE

      *------ REWRITE LOAN RECORD ------------------------------------*
           DISPLAY LOAN-REC
           REWRITE LOAN-REC
                  INVALID KEY
                        DISPLAY 'REWRITE FAILED'
           END-REWRITE.








